Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,☮[Phr0stYsuBs]☮ In the year 845...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the Colossal and Armored Titans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly appeared, destroying the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,along with the life we'd known.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity abandoned Wall Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,losing twenty percent of its population\Nand a third of its territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to retreat within Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.84,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,And in the year 850, in Trost...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:37.46,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Once again, humanity could\Nnot stop a Titan invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:42.18,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger had been\Ndevoured by a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:47.19,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,but reappeared, emerging\Nfrom a mysterious Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Response\NThe Battle for Trost (6)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll ask you once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:30.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.52,Default,E,0,0,0,,A human!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,Then don't hate me for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.14,Default,D,0,0,0,,Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.23,Default,D,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.58,Default,D,0,0,0,,I can't fight the Titans anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:53.86,Default,M,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.15,Default,D,0,0,0,,My friends were eaten\Nright in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.14,Default,D,0,0,0,,I saw them devoured,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.07,Default,D,0,0,0,,and I didn't even feel sad or angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.49,Default,D,0,0,0,,All I could think was,\N"I'm so glad that it wasn't me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.29,Default,D,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.64,Default,D,0,0,0,,Next time, it'll be me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.71,Default,D,0,0,0,,Essentially, our job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:16.13,Default,D,0,0,0,,is to fight the Titans\Nuntil they eat us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.47,Default,D,0,0,0,,I'd rather die right now than be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.13,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.30,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.34,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,You aren't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.55,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Everyone is struggling with that fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.43,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Look at Sasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after what happened,\Nshe is still a proud soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.88,Default,Sa,0,0,0,,I have a terrible stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,May I go join the wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.20,Default,D,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.95,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.15,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.99,Default,J,0,0,0,,I guess that gag order\Nwas indeed necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.87,Default,J,0,0,0,,Just look at them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.02,Default,J,0,0,0,,If they learn about Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.09,Default,R,0,0,0,,A cannon shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.05,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Why only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.64,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Look! Smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.18,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,From inside the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.71,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.94,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.29,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Did they break through the floodgate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.94,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,No way! That's the strongest part...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.30,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Someone just screwed up\Nand dropped a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.52,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,But why is there so much smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.70,Default,J,0,0,0,,It can't be... A Titan's steam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.70,Default,J,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.50,Default,J,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.06,Default,R,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.08,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,It's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.46,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,Captain Wellman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,J-Just look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.63,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Maintain your position\Nand remain on high alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Maintain your position!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,Have the gunners load another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.88,Default,E,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.35,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I remember hearing the cannon fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.56,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,And then there was a horrible\Nsound, a shock wave, and heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.60,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Are we inside a huge skeletonÃ¢Â€Â”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren protected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.27,Default,M,0,0,0,,That's all we need to know for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.99,Default,M,0,0,0,,Flowers survived, only inside...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:32.91,Default,E,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.79,Default,E,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.58,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.46,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.16,Default,E,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:43.63,Default,E,0,0,0,,But this thing will soon dissipate\Nlike any other Titan corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.67,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Let's get away from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.32,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Are they in shock, or just\Nwaiting to see what we'll do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.15,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The Garrison isn't doing\Nanything right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.59,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,They'll attack again before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.50,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,After showing them this, I doubt we'll\Nbe able to talk our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.17,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,But I do remember one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.60,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.11,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The basement of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.85,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Dad said that if I go there,\NI'll learn everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.45,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,This happened to me because of him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.34,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,If I go to the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably learn what\Nthe Titans really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.17,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.17,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Then why did he hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.97,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Isn't that information
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.72,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,what thousands of Survey\NCorps soldiers died for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it humanity's last hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:44.13,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,And he's been keeping it locked\Nin the basement of our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.61,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,What the hell was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.63,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Where the hell has he been\Nthe past five years, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.13,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.27,Default,M,0,0,0,,Right now, we have other priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.74,Default,E,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.37,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,The smoke's clearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.37,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,When you see them, attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.38,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Let's end this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.92,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.81,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.02,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Where will you go? And how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.85,Default,E,0,0,0,,For now, I don't care where.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.31,Default,E,0,0,0,,But from there, over the walls,\Nto the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.48,Default,E,0,0,0,,Once I become a Titan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.14,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.28,Default,E,0,0,0,,I don't know how I do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.42,Default,E,0,0,0,,But I still think I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:42.37,Default,E,0,0,0,,It's similar to the way you can't explain\Nhow you move your own arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.26,Default,E,0,0,0,,Back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,my only thought was stopping that shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:52.38,Default,E,0,0,0,,So that body had no other function and\Nrotted away after having served its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.72,Default,E,0,0,0,,This time, I'll turn\Ninto something stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A 15-meter class, like the one\Nthat tore apart those Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.16,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nose is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.50,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,You look pale, and your\Nbreaths are ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.44,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Your body is in bad shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.82,Default,E,0,0,0,,How I feel doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.87,Default,E,0,0,0,,I've come up with two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:25.99,Default,E,0,0,0,,First, if you don't try to protect me,\Nat least they won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.54,Default,E,0,0,0,,Although I've already\Ncaused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.05,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of leaving here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.38,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.82,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I'll go, tooÃ¢Â€Â”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:36.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:39.93,Default,E,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,If I can't keep up, you don't\Nneed to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,But I don't have to do what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.98,Default,E,0,0,0,,I've told you to stop all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.58,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'm not your little brother,\Nand I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Information We Can Share So Far: - Yeast (1) A special yeast made only within Wall Sina keeps fodder,\Nwheat, beans, and other items from spoiling for a long time when placed in storerooms or tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Information We Can Share So Far: - Yeast (2) By seeding storage caches\Nwith this yeast along supply lanes, humanity prepares to retake Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:09.04,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,Captain, the next round\Nwill be loaded soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we attack again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait for my signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.34,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:23.01,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The Garrison's giving no indication of\Nmoving to attack with their blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:28.39,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Mikasa's more sensitive than\Na stray cat to those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.59,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Loading the next round will probably take
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a minimum of another twenty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:38.40,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Before then, Eren will have\Nmade his move and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:46.76,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Why would I remember these\Nthings at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:52.08,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Is it because this is it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.38,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,And at the end, I was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing more than a coward, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.06,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,They saved me over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:10.35,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,but I was never able to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:18.53,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,As a friend, how can I stand\Non equal ground with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.86,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,How could I say I'd go with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.85,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,When even I'm not sure I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.63,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Now, the three of us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,will probably never\Nbe together again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.24,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.56,Default,E,0,0,0,,Wait, Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.30,Default,E,0,0,0,,I said I've come up with two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.76,Default,E,0,0,0,,Armin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.65,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'll let you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:03.83,Default,E,0,0,0,,I know what I've just\Nsaid isn't that realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.45,Default,E,0,0,0,,The smartest thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,would be to stay with the troops\Nand use this ability strategically.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.42,Default,E,0,0,0,,I know it's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:20.37,Default,E,0,0,0,,But if you think you can convince\Nthe Garrison I'm not a threat right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:24.03,Default,E,0,0,0,,I will trust your judgment\Nand follow your lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.43,Default,E,0,0,0,,That's my second option.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:31.81,Default,E,0,0,0,,If you say you can't, I'll do\Nwhat I described before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.52,Default,E,0,0,0,,You have fifteen seconds to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.97,Default,E,0,0,0,,Whether or not you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.33,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'll respect your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.41,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:51.07,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Why would you entrust\Nme with this choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.02,Default,E,0,0,0,,Whenever things get really bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you always know the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.96,Default,E,0,0,0,,And I want to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.46,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,When have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.58,Default,E,0,0,0,,There have been plenty of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:09.00,Default,E,0,0,0,,Five years ago, if you\Nhadn't called Hannes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.43,Default,E,0,0,0,,Titans would have eaten Mikasa and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.74,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Was it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.13,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,just in my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:31.68,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Only I thought that I was useless?\NThat I was just slowing them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:38.76,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,These two never thought\Nthat for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.20,Default,E,0,0,0,,Armin, we're out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.76,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,Looks like the next round is loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.51,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,We can fire any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.19,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,These two are putting\Ntheir lives in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:56.13,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The two people I trust\Nmost in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:01.29,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,What could be more convincing than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.97,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I will persuade them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:10.98,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The two of you, avoid doing anything\Nthat'd make them think you're a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.89,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Ever since Eren became\Na Titan and fought for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,something has been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.97,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I don't have it all clear in\Nmy head, but I'll do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:28.22,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I'll figure it out while I speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:33.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,You've finally shown\Nyour true self, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll give the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.71,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,He is not an enemy of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:52.20,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,We are prepared to share\Nall the information we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in hearing\Nyou plead for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:58.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,How can I believe you, when he's\Nshown us all what he really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,If you say he's not an\Nenemy, then prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,If you can't, I'll be forced\Nto eliminate the threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.79,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,There is no need for proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.60,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,That's right... We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:14.63,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The question isn't what we think of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:15.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.48,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I'm told that many of you saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:22.04,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Then you saw him fighting the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:25.52,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,And you saw the Titans swarm him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:32.70,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,That means the Titans considered him\Nfood, the same way they think of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:37.70,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is the truth, no matter\Nwhat we may think or believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.33,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.95,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,A Titan as an ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.34,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:49.34,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,But if we could control a Titan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,Prepare to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled by their clever lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,The Titans' actions have always\Nbeen beyond our understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:09.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's possible they could\Npretend to be human,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,speak human languages,\Nand try to deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,We can't let them get\Naway with anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.52,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.12,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,He isn't even trying to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.10,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,He's scared of thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.29,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren... Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.39,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I am a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore long ago to dedicate\Nmy life to the revival of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:50.78,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,If that pursuit were to cost\Nme my life, I would be glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:55.74,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,If we use his Titan powers and\Nthe forces we still have,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.90,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,we could take back this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.16,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,With my final breath before my death,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall wish for humanity's glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:07.13,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,and try to persuade you\Nof his strategic value!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.05,Default,Ian,0,0,0,,Captain Wellman, I believe\Nwe should considerÃ¢Â€Â”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,Their pleas are irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,They are traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Anyone who violates the\Nrules must be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,That is my duty as a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.65,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:38.66,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,As big as you are, you've always been\Nas delicate as a newborn fawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,Commander Pixis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:47.37,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Do you not see his splendid salute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.27,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I've just arrived, but messengers have\Nkept me abreast of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.00,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,You go command the reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:02.26,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I think we should listen to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:12.00,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Reports by the Survey Corps had said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the Titans would come from the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:19.43,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,In fact, it was Zhiganshina District,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,south of Wall Maria, that was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:28.54,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Thus, it was widely believed that\Nthe district south of Wall Rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Trost, had the highest likelihood\Nof being the next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Trost District, Inner Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.28,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Dot Pixis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.93,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,He is the High Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of the entire southern\Nregion, including Trost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.37,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,The man with absolute authority over
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the defense of humanity's\Nmost important region.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.98,Default,P,0,0,0,,No luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:59.80,Default,P,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind being eaten by a\Nreally beautiful Titan woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.20,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,And he is known to be a total eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,What is the Commander thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,Allowing them up there unguarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,when we don't know what they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.13,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:17.43,Default,Riko,0,0,0,,The Commander's ideas are always\Nbeyond normal people's comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.59,Default,Ian,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.45,Default,Ian,0,0,0,,The squads are in formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.82,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we reach this basement,\Nwe'll understand everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.77,Default,E,0,0,0,,Yes... Will you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.32,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,As long as you, yourself,\Nlack absolute conviction,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't promise more than\Nthat I'll keep it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:48.70,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,But I do take pride in being able to\Nrecognize the truth of what I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:52.50,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I'll guarantee your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.73,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Trainee Arlert, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.77,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:02.76,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Back there, you said we could use
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the Titan's power to reclaim this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.14,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Did you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.27,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Or was it just a plea to save your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:13.67,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.81,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:19.35,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,What I meant was to have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren become a Titan,\Nthen move that boulder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to seal the destroyed gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.50,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,But it was just an idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.40,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I thought I could get them to at least
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,at least consider using Eren's power\Nto find a way out of our predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.52,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Of course, I wanted to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.30,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,You wanted to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.05,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I can trust those words\Nmore than any others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:01.61,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Well, Trainee Jaeger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:03.20,Default,E,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.87,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Can you seal that hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.10,Default,E,0,0,0,,Well... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.23,Default,E,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:18.52,Default,E,0,0,0,,I don't know much more than\Neveryone else here does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.50,Default,E,0,0,0,,So... whether I can do it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.73,Default,E,0,0,0,,I can't answer you for\Nsure when I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.17,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:28.50,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.91,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,I asked the wrong question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:35.85,Default,Pi,0,0,0,,Will you do it? Or won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.66,Default,E,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:12.51,Default,E,0,0,0,,I don't know whether\NI can seal the hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,But I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they had fled out of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:24:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,soldiers choose to stand\Nonce more on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren decides to become everyone's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Icon The Battle for Trost (7)
